          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-answer">O <strong>placa video rtx 4070</strong> are un consum TDP (Thermal Design Power) de aproximativ 200W. Nvidia recomanda o sursa de alimentare de minim 650W, insa o sursa de 750W ofera mai multa siguranta si eficienta.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-item">
        <div class="faq-question">
          ce probleme pot aparea la o placa video rtx 4070
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-answer">Problemele comune pot fi legate de dimensiunea placii (necesita o carcasa spatioasa), necesitatea unui conector de alimentare specific (12VHPWR) si, ca la orice placa, necesitatea unei surse de alimentare adecvate si a unei raciri bune in carcasa pentru a evita supraincalzirea.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-item">
        <div class="faq-question">
